Author: hopeless_anon
Text: ugh I'm in a bit of an unspoken competition with my bitch of a roommate. She keeps bragging about being thin and having low bodyfat and not being hungry. She has "food intollerances" too and ugh. I'm like a little skinnier than her but I need to lose 10lbs so I can prove I'm not a piece of trash loser like she thinks I am. ughhh I hate these type of things it's so triggering but also so motivating??
